</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-egiyK kKHsVi pf-82_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-ilfuhL ejXpQB pf-83_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-dtMgUX gYEGeC pf-84_ pf-heading-1-h3">Recommendations
</h3><p class="sc-cZMNgc hqfPHB pf-86_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">For educational institutions aiming to align with EWC standards, the following steps are recommended:



























</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-bQtKYq czWvgn pf-88_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-89_ pf-text-1"><strong>Integrate EWC guidelines into policies</strong> - Ensure that institutional policies reflect EWC standards and guidelines, making them a part of everyday practice.

</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-91_ pf-text-1"><strong>Utilise technology for compliance</strong> - Implement compliance management software like ComplyPlus™ to streamline the monitoring and management of regulatory requirements.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-93_ pf-text-1"><strong>Engage with the EWC </strong>- Regularly consult the EWC for updates and guidance, ensuring that your institution complies with the latest standards.













</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-egiyK kKHsVi pf-95_ pf-r pf-c-lm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-ilfuhL ejXpQB pf-96_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-dtMgUX gYEGeC pf-97_ pf-heading-1-h3">Conclusion
